      "status": "todo",
      "title": "Add scenario-level app parity coverage",
      "description": "Expand app parity tracking beyond top-level command presence so it catches the actual cross-surface drift found in the audit: loop summaries, stop behavior, custom queue paths, plugin/native controls, and continuation actions. The parity source should describe user-visible scenarios and point to Rust plus RalphMac tests that prove each surface stays aligned.",
