        "Update app parity output to report missing scenario coverage clearly without treating GitHub Actions as a canonical CI gate.",
        "Record any meaningful parity-governance decision in the nearest existing project source of truth.",
        "Run targeted parity tests plus `make agent-ci` if the implementation changes code."
